  "notebookEntry": {
    "content": "<h2>Tlak</h2><p><strong>Tlak</strong> vyjadřuje, jak velká síla působí na jednotku plochy.</p><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 420 150' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'><text x='210' y='18' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='13'>Tlak závisí na ploše</text><rect x='30' y='90' width='150' height='8' fill='#d1d5db' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><rect x='80' y='40' width='50' height='50' rx='5' fill='#dbeafe' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2'/><text x='105' y='70' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='11'>F</text><line x1='105' y1='90' x2='105' y2='115' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='2.5'/><text x='105' y='130' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444' font-size='10'>velká plocha</text><text x='105' y='145' text-anchor='middle' fill='#22c55e' font-size='10' font-weight='bold'>malý tlak</text><rect x='270' y='90' width='150' height='8' fill='#d1d5db' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><rect x='330' y='40' width='20' height='50' rx='3' fill='#dbeafe' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2'/><text x='340' y='70' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='11'>F</text><line x1='340' y1='90' x2='340' y2='115' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='2.5'/><text x='340' y='130' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444' font-size='10'>malá plocha</text><text x='340' y='145' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444' font-size='10' font-weight='bold'>velký tlak!</text></svg></div><h3>Vzorec</h3><div class='formula'>$$p = \\frac{F}{S}$$</div><table><thead><tr><th>Veličina</th><th>Symbol</th><th>Jednotka</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>tlak</td><td>p</td><td>Pa (pascal)</td></tr><tr><td>síla</td><td>F</td><td>N (newton)</td></tr><tr><td>obsah plochy</td><td>S</td><td>m²</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Odvozené vzorce</h3><div class='formula'>$$F = p \\cdot S$$</div><div class='formula'>$$S = \\frac{F}{p}$$</div><h3>Jednotky tlaku</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Jednotka</th><th>Převod</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1 Pa</td><td>1 N/m²</td></tr><tr><td>1 kPa</td><td>1 000 Pa</td></tr><tr><td>1 hPa</td><td>100 Pa</td></tr><tr><td>1 atm</td><td>101 325 Pa</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Příklad</h3><p>Na desku o obsahu 0,5 m² působí síla 200 N. Jaký je tlak?</p><p><strong>Řešení:</strong></p><div class='formula'>$$p = \\frac{F}{S} = \\frac{200}{0{,}5} = 400 \\, \\text{Pa}$$</div>"
  }
}
